  "description": "<i>Command &amp; Conquer: Red Alert - Retaliation</i> combines the campaigns seen in the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/windows/command-conquer-red-alert\">Command & Conquer: Red Alert</a> PC add-ons <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/command-conquer-red-alert-counterstrike\">Counterstrike</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/command-conquer-red-alert-the-aftermath\">The Aftermath</a> into one complete game for the PlayStation. It also continues the same storyline seen in the original <i>Red Alert</i>.<br><br>New additions include specially produced cutscenes, an improved interface for the control pad users, and a special two player mode, where two PlayStations can be connected using the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?attribute=Link+Cable\">link cable</a> and two TVs. Inserting one of the disks into one of the consoles results in playing a 2 player version of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Command+%26+Conquer+Red+Alert+series\">Red Alert</a>, with 100 different missions to play.\n",
